import React from 'react'
import ContentLoader from "react-content-loader"

export const Preloader = props => (

		height={150}
		width={500}
		speed={2}
		primaryColor="#4c90f3"
		secondaryColor="#ecebeb"
		{...props}
	>

		<rect x="81" y="1" rx="3" ry="3" width="100" height="10" />

		<rect x="299.63" y="62.61" rx="0" ry="0" width="249" height="10" />
	</ContentLoader>
